<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>퀴즈 시작</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      width: 100vw;
      min-height: 100dvh; /* ✅ 모바일 주소창 높이 반영 */
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-image: url('/answers.png');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center top;
      background-size: contain; /* ✅ 이미지 전체가 잘리지 않게 */
      background-color: #000;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px #000;
    }

    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      padding: 20px 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    input {
      width: 250px;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 6px 0;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 15px;
      padding: 10px 25px;
      font-size: 18px;
      background-color: #ff5555;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #ff3333;
    }

    /* 📱 모바일 대응 */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body {
        background-size: contain; /* 이미지 전체 표시 */
        background-position: center top;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      input {
        width: 200px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>내 기억과 관련된 것들을  <br>찾았나? </h2>
  <form method="POST" action="/submit">
    <% for (let i = 1; i <= 10; i++) { %>
      <input type="text" name="answer<%= i %>" placeholder="정답 <%= i %>">
    <% } %>
    <button type="submit">제출</button>
  </form>
</body>
</html>
